Class UnsupportedKeySizeException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • psi.exception.UnsupportedKeySizeException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UnsupportedKeySizeException
extends java.lang.Exception
    This exception is thrown whenever the server attempts to initialize a session with an unsupported key size, or when a client attempts to load a session associated to an unsupported key size.
